  <Properties />
  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[The Example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>There is <strong>SearchTextBox </strong>control on the <em>Form</em>.<br />Click on the 'Arrow' button to show the <strong>DropDownMenu</strong>.<br />In the menu you can either set search text from one of the top searches or choose search engine to use.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p><strong>DropDownMenu </strong>property gets or sets the dropdown menu for <strong>SearchTextBox </strong>control</p><p>Property type: Gizmox.WebGui.Forms.<strong>ContextMenu</strong></p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>